714447f-a.title: Manhattan: 75th Street (East) - Lexington Avenue
714447f-a.text:
East 75th Street, north side, west from Lexington
to Park Avenues, showing prominently the Park Anlex
Garage. This bears No. 115-9 and adjoining the N. W.
corner of Lexington Avenue.
October 11, 1927
P. L. Sperr, pho.
NO REPRODUCTITNS
